    "The number of training instances per episode in the metacontroller is set to k=60.",
    "In our experiments, we observed the performance of the meta-controller for k=10,20, 30, 60 and 120.",
    "Based on the loss and the accuracy of the model, we set the k=60 in our final experiments.",
    "The model contains a feed-forward layer with a SGD optimizer and it updates every 8 episodes.",
    "Once the importance score for all attentions in each batch has been calculated, we use the Gumbel-softmax to generate a vector representation, which ensures that the modification in attention weights maintains the similarity between the original and pruned models."
